#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ksirk; is a computerized version of a well known strategy game. "
#| "Commercial and other Free Software versions exist but I (Gaël de "
#| "Chalendar) created this game initially as a C++ learning exercise and so, "
#| "I developed it up to this point (see README for details)."
msgid ""
"&ksirk; is a computerized version of a well known strategy game. Commercial "
"and other Free Software versions exist but I (Gaël de Chalendar) created "
"this game initially as a C++ learning exercise and so, I developed it up to "
"this point (see <filename>README</filename> for details)."
msgstr ""
"&ksirk; on tuntud strateegiamängu arvutiversioon. Sellest on olemas nii "
"kommerts- kui ka teisi vaba tarkvara versioone, kuid mina (Gael de "
"Chalendar) lõin selle mängu esialgu C++ programmeerimiskeele õppimiseks ning "
"olen sealtpeale seda aina arendanud (täpsemalt kõneleb sellest fail README)."

