#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ksirk; comes with a skin editor, named ksirkskineditor(!), that allows "
#| "to edit all skin data, as soon as graphics (map, sprites, &etc;) are "
#| "available in a SVG file. Please see the ksirkskineditor manual for "
